<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('../partials/head', { title }) %></head>
<body class="page-impact">
<%- include('../partials/header', { activePage }) %>

<main class="impact-main">
  <section class="impact-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="impact-hero-card">
        <div class="impact-hero-photo" role="img" aria-label="Zambian marketplace at sunrise with entrepreneurs at work">
          <div class="impact-hero-scene" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="impact-scene-sun"></span>
            <span class="impact-scene-stall impact-scene-stall-a"></span>
            <span class="impact-scene-stall impact-scene-stall-b"></span>
            <span class="impact-scene-skyline"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-hero-copy">
          <span class="impact-pill">Maturity &amp; Growth</span>
          <h1>Our Impact</h1>
          <p class="impact-lead">
            Building the foundations of Zambia's future economy through structured support.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="impact-intro">
    <div class="container impact-intro-inner">
      <h2>Creating Connected Businesses</h2>
      <p>
        Moovex isn't just about ideas on paper—it's about architecture. We transform fragmented local businesses
        into organized, connected, and capable companies that drive sustainable employment across Zambia.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="impact-metrics">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="impact-metrics-bento">
        <div class="impact-metrics-row">
          <article class="impact-metric-card impact-metric-gradient">
            <div class="impact-metric-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M10 2h4a2 2 0 012 2v2h4v16H4V6h4V4a2 2 0 012-2zm2 4V4h-2v2h2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <strong>Entrepreneurship</strong>
            <span>Support</span>
          </article>

          <article class="impact-metric-card impact-metric-gradient">
            <div class="impact-metric-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3s-1.34-3-3-3-3 1.34-3 3 1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3S9.66 5 8 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5C15 14.17 10.33 13 8 13zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <strong>Future</strong>
            <span>Impact reporting</span>
          </article>
        </div>

        <article class="impact-feature-card">
          <div class="impact-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 3L1 12h3v8h6v-6h2v6h6v-8h3L12 3zm0 2.8L17 12h-2v6h-2v-6H9.8L12 5.8z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <strong>Multiple business sectors</strong>
          <p>Connected across transport, digital services, retail, e-banking access, and property management in the Moovex ecosystem.</p>
          <div class="impact-progress" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="impact-progress-fill"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="impact-progress-labels">
            <span>Impact tracking in progress</span>
            <span>Future impact reporting</span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="impact-stories">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="impact-stories-heading">
        <h2>Voices of Growth</h2>
        <p>Stories we are building across the Moovex ecosystem.</p>
      </header>

      <article class="impact-story-card">
        <div class="impact-story-photo" role="img" aria-label="GetPro call center and digital workspace">
          <div class="impact-story-scene" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="impact-story-figure"></span>
            <span class="impact-story-screen"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-story-body">
          <div class="impact-story-label">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2l2.2 6.8H21l-5.5 4 2.1 6.7L12 16.8 6.4 20l2.1-6.7L3 9.3h6.8L12 2z"></path></svg>
            <span>Success Spotlight</span>
          </div>
          <h3>GetPro Digital Services</h3>
          <p class="impact-story-placeholder">Placeholder — representative ecosystem example, not a verified testimonial.</p>
          <p class="impact-story-quote">
            GetPro is part of the Moovex ecosystem, providing call center and digital agency services that help
            local businesses improve customer service, business processes, websites, apps, and social media presence.
          </p>
          <div class="impact-story-author">
            <div class="impact-story-avatar" aria-hidden="true">GP</div>
            <div>
              <p class="impact-story-name">GetPro</p>
              <p class="impact-story-role">Call Center &amp; Digital Agency · Ecosystem partner</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="impact-action">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="impact-action-card">
        <h2>Your Support in Action</h2>
        <ul class="impact-action-list">
          <li>
            <span class="impact-action-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5 13.18v4L12 21l7-3.82v-4L12 17l-7-3.82zM12 3L1 9l11 6 9-4.91V17h2V9L12 3z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4>Specialized Training</h4>
              <p>Sustaining technical mentorship for emerging business leaders across the Moovex ecosystem.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="impact-action-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 6h18V4H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h14v-2H4V6zm13 6H9v2h8v-2zm0-4H9v2h8V8z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4>Digital Infrastructure</h4>
              <p>Providing digital tools and essential business systems to streamline operations.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="impact-action-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20 6h-4V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h16a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2zM10 4h4v2h-4V4zm6 13H8v-2h8v2z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <h4>Job Creation</h4>
              <p>Supporting internship and work programs that lead to career placement and local services.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/partner" class="impact-btn">Partner With Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
